{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d1b02d24-9538-4ee4-8422-f676507ba0c3","content":"I can help you analyze a .NET crash dump! I don't have a specialized skill for dump analysis, but I can assist using `dotnet-dump analyze` or `lldb` with the SOS debugging extension.\n\nTo get started, I need a few details:\n\n1. **Where is the .dmp file located?** (path on this system, or do you need to upload it?)\n2. **Which .NET version** is the app targeting? (.NET 6/7/8/9, or .NET Framework?)\n3. **What platform** was the app running on when it crashed? (Windows/Linux)\n\nIn the meantime, here's the general approach I'd take:\n\n- Use `dotnet-dump analyze` to inspect managed threads, exceptions, and the call stack\n- Run SOS commands like `!pe` (print exception), `!clrstack`, `!threads`, and `!dumpheap` to identify the crash cause\n\nWould you like me to check if `dotnet-dump` is available in this environment while you provide the file path?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"51cf0638-fe55-4034-ab18-31ed72d6357b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a .dmp crash dump file from a .NET application and wants to analyze it to find the root cause of the crash. Let me look at the available skills to see if any are relevant.\n\nLooking at the available skills:\n- `dump-collect` - This is for **collecting** crash dumps, NOT analyzing them. The description explicitly says \"DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\"\n- `dotnet-trace-collect` - This is for capturing diagnostic artifacts, not analyzing dumps\n- `android-tombstone-symbolication` - For Android tombstones, not .dmp files\n\n\n- `apple-crash-symbolication` - For Apple .ips crash logs, not .dmp files\n\nNone of the available skills are designed for analyzing .dmp files. I could help directly using `dotnet-dump analyze` if the .NET tools are available in the environment, or I can guide them through the analysis process manually.","outputTokens":571,"requestId":"C3C7:86E8:1D29D05:20CF1D7:6A07C3F0"},"id":"de74570d-6cf3-4be1-a491-fcc62d3687a0","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:10:22.160Z","parentId":"20e2dfe1-352d-46ea-9df0-b76c8d34941a"}
